## Guiding Principles

- No separate VPN client software layer, no additional helper apps
- Easy enough for kids and grandparents to use
- Easy for parents to admin
- Secure defaults, easy first run.
- Keep setup boring: one DNS record, one compose path, minimal config.


## Before announcing

- Pairing/approval/auth flows are stable and test-covered.
- Upgrade availability is obvious in admin and notifications.

## Priority Roadmap

- Add admin action to revoke all active sessions.
- Add import/export/backup guidance in admin and docs.

2) Deny reason visibility
- Surface explicit auth decision reasons in logs and admin UI:
  - pending device
  - invalid signature
  - stale/invalid timestamp
  - unknown device
  - invalid session proof

3) Test foundation
- Expand tests for:
  - happy path pairing -> approval -> access
